Class Coins

  • java.lang.Object
    • Coins

  • public class Coins
extends java.lang.Object
    Based on the values of five kinds of coins, class Coins calculate the total value of the coins and display the number of each coins.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Zhi Heng Zhu
